    WithExampleSchema<List<Object>>

    public class CrestArraySchema
extends com.fasterxml.jackson.module.jsonSchema.types.ArraySchema
implements WithExampleSchema<List<Object>>
    An extension to the Jackson ArraySchema that includes the custom CREST JSON Schema attributes.
